            . I am a fishmonger. On the 13th of March, between four and five o'clock, I was by Hughes's house, at <placeName id="t18220417-161-crimeloc841">Somers Town</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18220417-161-crimeloc841" type="placeName" value="Somers Town"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18220417-161-crimeloc841" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-161-off839 t18220417-161-crimeloc841"></join>, and saw the prisoner take a copper from his door, put it on his head, and walk off with it. I pointed him out to White, who took him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-161-person1534">
                  SOPHIA 
                  WHITE
               <interp inst="t18220417-161-person1534" type="surname" value="WHITE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220417-161-person1534" type="given" value="SOPHIA"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220417-161-person1534" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . Lodge alarmed me; I ran up the street, and seized the prisoner with the copper on his head. He said it was not mine.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-161-person1535">
                  JAMES 
                  WHITE
               <interp inst="t18220417-161-person1535" type="surname" value="WHITE"></interp>
